---
description: Generate summary reports for reviews
mlld-version: ">=1.0.0-rc"
---

# Summary Report Template

>> Create a summary report of the review process
@text createSummaryReport(prData, validation, review) = [[
## 📊 Review Summary

### Pull Request
- **PR**: #{{prData.number}} - {{prData.title}}
- **Author**: @{{prData.author.login}}
- **Files**: {{prData.files.length}} changed

### Validation
- **Status**: {{validation.valid ? "✅ Passed" : "❌ Failed"}}
- **Checks**: {{validation.checkedFields}} fields validated
{{validation.issues.length > 0 ? "- **Issues**: " + validation.issues.length + " found" : ""}}

### Review Decision
- **Recommendation**: {{review.recommendation}}
- **Type**: {{review.error ? "Fallback (AI unavailable)" : "AI Review"}}

### Module Info
{{validation.moduleData.name ? "- **Name**: `" + validation.moduleData.name + "`" : ""}}
{{validation.moduleData.author ? "- **Author**: " + validation.moduleData.author : ""}}
{{validation.moduleData.description ? "- **Description**: " + validation.moduleData.description : ""}}

---
*Review completed at {{new Date().toISOString()}}*
]]

@data module = {
  "createSummaryReport": @createSummaryReport
}